        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1047036770" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1047036770" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1047036770">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/slows/">慢慢的光</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2016-07-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本书里面的内容在国内的新闻记者类的书中有少涉及，很新鲜。但这本书写得太长，导致前面还能认真多，到后面只能是略读了。也许因为我不是记者的缘故。但这本书如果写得短一点，我也许会读得更多。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="266095636">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-266095636" class="vote-count">0</span>
